528
00:36:51.920 --> 00:36:54.464
And we're gonna figure this out. Okay?

529
00:36:56.884 --> 00:36:59.803
Well. you should probably shower first.

530
00:37:00.721 --> 00:37:02.890
- You stink.
- Thank you. Good note.

531
00:37:05.309 --> 00:37:06.310
Anything else?

532
00:37:08.395 --> 00:37:09.855
