574
00:40:52.077 --> 00:40:53.221
I'm under some pressure.

575
00:40:53.245 --> 00:40:54.639
- but I'm perfectly…
- you assaulted that woman.

576
00:40:54.663 --> 00:40:55.723
She hit me first!

577
00:40:55.747 --> 00:40:59.185
Whoa. Is that what I'm supposed
